==Chinese==

===Etymology===
Literally: Give three orders and five explanations.

===Pronunciation===
====[[wikipedia:Standard_Mandarin|Mandarin]]====
[[Pinyin]]: sān lìng wŭ shēn
====[[wikipedia:Min Nan|Min Nan]]====
[[wikipedia:POJ|POJ]]: sam-lēng-ngó•-sin

===Idiom===
'''[[三]][[令]][[五]][[申]]'''

# To repeatedly [[admonish]].
# To repeatedly [[warn]].

#: ''[[尽管]][[你]]'''三令五申'''，[[有]][[许多]][[员工]][[就是]][[不]][[肯]][[照办]].'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

#: ''[[儘管]][[你]]'''三令五申'''，[[有]][[許多]][[員工]][[就是]][[不]][[肯]][[照辦]].'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

